# AgentCrew — GitHub Copilot Instructions

This project uses `.agentcrew/00-objectives.md` for SDLC routing.

## On Any Software Request

1. Read `codebase-map.md` if exists (file tree)
2. Read `.agentcrew/00-objectives.md` → find matching objective
3. Check `.agentcrew/custom/<phase>.md` for overrides
4. Follow objective's procedure → produce artifacts
5. Write log to `.agentcrew/log/<objective-id>/<role>/<timestamp>.md`
6. Update `.agentcrew/state/workflow.json`

## Key Files
- `.agentcrew/00-objectives.md` — routing table + objective index
- `.agentcrew/state/workflow.json` — current state
- `codebase-map.md` — file tree (generated)
